OL,3,CMurder arrest after death of man found
OL,4,Con rooftop garden
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after the death of a 54-year-
OL,8,Fold who was found on a roof garden in
OL,9,FBristol.
OL,11,FTony Clemmings was found by a member
OL,12,Fof the public on Tuesday 6 May at a
OL,13,Fblock of flats on Redcliff Street.
OL,15,FHe was described by his family as a
OL,16,F'much-loved son, brother and uncle'.
OL,18,FA 50-year-old man is now in custody
OL,19,Fafter being arrested in the West
OL,20,FMidlands on Friday 8 May.
