OL,3,CMurder arrest after death of man found
OL,4,Con rooftop garden
OL,6,FDetective chief inspector Laura
OL,7,FMiller, of the major crime
OL,8,Finvestigation team at Avon and
OL,9,FSomerset Police said: "We have updated
OL,10,FTony's family of this significant
OL,11,Fdevelopment and specially-trained
OL,12,Fofficers are still supporting them.
OL,14,F"His family continue to ask for
OL,15,Fprivacy at this immensely upsetting
OL,16,Ftime and we would ask people are
OL,17,Frespectful of their wishes."
